<title>科学史：给出了110个高斯定理？看数学王子高斯的学霸人生！</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/k6QjXMOsn1</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/k6QjXMOsn1</guid>
<description>&lt;div id=&quot;img-content&quot; class=&quot;paper rich_media_area_primary &quot; readability=&quot;5.1578947368421&quot;&gt;

                        

                        
                            
&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
                                                    &lt;h2 class=&quot;common_share_title&quot;&gt;
                      
科学史：给出了110个高斯定理？看数学王子高斯的学霸人生！
                    &lt;/h2&gt;
                                  
                                          &lt;/p&gt;
                        

                        &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

                    &lt;div class=&quot;post-meta&quot;&gt;
